1. Create a Database name as Products and table as Product Details

    a. Product details should have following fields like Product ID, Product Name, Product Price

    b. Apply constraints and for Product Price it should allow only price greater than 10.

    c. Show the details of table as a proof of constraints applied


create database Products;
use Products;
show tables;

create table product_details(
product_id tinyint primary key,
product_name varchar(20) not null,
product_price int check (product_price > 10)
);

 select*from product_details;
